fields.Title: APT / REAL ESTATE AGENT
fields.Description: A short conversation with the real estate agent. She tells you about some apartments.

fields.Title: You: ""I fuck shit up too.""

You: ""Reprehensible. Who lived here?""

fields.Title: Real Estate Agent: ""Thank you." She slips the passport..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thank you." She slips the passport back in her purse. "Do you have any questions? I need to be back in midtown in an hour."

fields.Title: Real Estate Agent: ""What now?" She crosses her arms im..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What now?" She crosses her arms impatiently.

fields.Title: Empathy: "Her voice is really cheerful despit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her voice is really cheerful despite her obviously *hating* you.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "It's as if they're *real* wizards,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's as if they're *real* wizards, able to resurrect dead real estate and breathe life into bank accounts.

fields.Title: Real Estate Agent: ""Everyone says that real estate age..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Everyone says that real estate agents don't *do* anything, but here I am, in the middle of the night, cleaning up someone's 'crash pad'."

fields.Title: Endurance: "Come to think of it, she *does* loo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Come to think of it, she *does* look incredibly tired.

fields.Title: Real Estate Agent: ""Oh, that's another huge mess. The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, that's another huge mess. The former tenant owes us three months of rent, *three*! We closed the apartment and planned on auctioning off the valuables, but..."

fields.Title: Real Estate Agent: ""*Both* apartments are now unrentab..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Both* apartments are now unrentable. Both!" She's still shaking her head, manicured hands now crossed over the chest.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Boy there are a lot of different ke..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Boy there are a lot of different keys there. More than *twenty* at least...

fields.Title: Real Estate Agent: ""It *is*." She breathes in and out..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It *is*." She breathes in and out to the count of three -- it looks like some special stress release technique -- before she continues...

fields.Title: Real Estate Agent: ""So, the sooner we get this over wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So, the sooner we get this over with, the better." She means you -- time for the next question.

fields.Title: Real Estate Agent: ""Do you want to see my ID as well?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you want to see my ID as well? You can't *legally* ask for it, but why not? Want to see my residence permit, too?" She fumbles through her purse, fishing out a light paper-clad passport.

fields.Title: Real Estate Agent: ""These apartments are perfectly fin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "These apartments are perfectly fine! They have gorgeous architecture, a million reál view of the bay, good ventilation, neighbours, life, spark... And they are affordable."

fields.Title: Real Estate Agent: ""I'll tell you, Martinaise has a fu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'll tell you, Martinaise has a future -- in a few years it's going to blossom with artists and creatives and those radiocomputer wizards."

fields.Title: You: ""It couldn't have been that much mo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It couldn't have been that much money. These apartments look pretty shabby."
